name: Tim Nelson
hometown: Wherever the strategy pattern is used
bio: Good to meet you all! I'm a first-generation college student who attended community college, a commuter-focused state college, the 'college' of an industry job, a STEM university, and... now teaches at Brown. Someone who enjoys puns might call this a collage of colleges, although not quite a universe of universities.

name: Roberto Gonzales
bio: Hiii everyone, I’m Roberto, a senior studying CS. I love playing guitar, crocheting, roof climbing, and breakdancing. Feel free to reach out if you want to chat or if you think you can beat me in Mario Kart.

name: Annie Ye
bio: Hi! I’m a senior from San Francisco studying Computer Science. I like hitting back and bi at the gym, drinking overpriced matcha, and listening to Frank Ocean. Super excited to meet you all!

name: Sana Saab
bio: Hi! I'm Sana, and I'm a junior from Michigan studying CS. I like learning new types of dance (albeit badly), trying out new clubs and hobbies, and going on adventures!

name: Joshua Bala
bio: Heyyy, my name is Joshua Bala and I'm a Junior studying cs. Big fan of basketball, anime, boba and any apple deserts. Also I dabble in hiking and biking. Very excited for this semester and TAing this class!!!!!!!

name: Sophia Lim
bio: Hi!! I'm Sophia from Auckland, New Zealand and I'm studying CS-Econ. I love baking, beaches, and travelling to new places. This is my second semester TAing CS32 and I am super excited to meet you all <3

name: Emily Wang
bio: Hi! I'm a senior from the Chicago suburbs studying CS. I love noodles, crochet, and playing Ghibli music on violin. Excited to meet everyone! :D

name: Aisosa Idahosa
bio: Hi everyone! I'm a sophomore from the Philly area studying CS and (maybe) MCM. In my free time, I love reading, crocheting, and recently I've been getting into ceramics! Super excited to TA this class and meet all of y'all!

name: Julie Chung
hometown: West Hartford, CT & New York, NY
bio: Hi everyone! My name is Julie, and I'm a senior from West Hartford, CT & New York, NY. I love to make music, cook, and play tennis (not great, but trying to get better). My recently developed hobby is meal prepping. I accept any and all cooking advice. Super excited to meet everyone!

name: Asia Nguyen
bio: Hi everyone! My name is Asia, and I'm a senior from Nashville studying CS + IAPA. I love reading, getting sweet treats, and going to concerts! I'm looking forward to this semester and meeting you all!

name: Alison Zeng
bio: Hi! I'm a junior studying Computer Science and Linguistics. Some things that are bringing me joy as of late are biking, writing (mostly poetry, occasional prose), and comedy panel shows.

name: Anant Saraf
bio: Hi everyone! I'm Anant, a 4th year in the Brown | RISD program studying CS and Photography from Kolkata, India. I love making images, playing video games, caffeine, watching music videos w friends, and being on the main green. Excited to meet you all!
